show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/ZPBYpu
show.description: Tulsi's loveless marriage to Aman Modi shatters when his manipulative friend Tanvi frames her for attempting to murder Baa. Cast out and humiliated, Tulsi transforms herself with childhood friend Bhavin's help, becoming a successful designer. When Aman discovers Tanvi's treachery—fake pregnancy, murder plots, and stolen designs—he publicly exposes her and reunites with Tulsi, finally recognizing her true worth.
